==English==

===Etymology===
From {{L.}} ''[[impellere]]''

===Verb===
{{en-infl-reg-consonant|impel||l}}

# {{transitive}} To [[drive]] [[forward]]; to [[propel]] an object, or to [[urge]] a person; to [[press]] on; to [[incite]] to [[action]] or [[motion]] in any way.

====Antonyms====
*[[expel]]

====Related terms====
*[[impellent]]
*[[impeller]]
*[[impulse]]

